				\begin{document}$$P_{{\mathrm{min}}} = T(v\,{\mathrm{sin}}\alpha + v_{\mathrm{i}}),$$\end{document}where vi is the induced velocity required for a given thrust and can be found by the solution to the implicit equation:7vi=2TπnD2ρvcosα2+vsinα+vi2.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
